            <div class="col-md-6 col-12">
                <h1>1. SoNet</h1>
                <p id="important">
                    This meticulously crafted <u>forum social media app</u> serves as a testament to my abilities, offering a large array of features. 
                    I invite you to experience the application as a demo user.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Functionality:
                    <ul>
                        <li>User registration and authentication</li>
                        <li>Profile customization</li>
                        <li>Post creation, modification, and deletion (latter two only if you're the author)</li>
                        <li>Like a post with live feedback</li>
                        <li>Comment on posts and reply to previous comments</li>
                        <li>Display nested comments</li>
                        <li>View users' pages with account infomation and all posts</li>
                        <li>Follow and unfollow other accounts</li>
                        <li>View a users following and followers list</li>
                        <li>Categorize posts into set categories</li>
                        <li>Sort posts by category, upload date, comment count, or like count</li>
                        <li>Remember sorting filter when page is redirected</li>
                        <li>Search by keywords (scans posts, comments, categories, and usernames)</li>
                        <li>An array of different pagination techniques</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
                <div class="project_buttons">
                    <button class="btn btn-lg project">View Project</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-lg source">Source Code</button>
                </div>
